# ============================================================
# CIVILIZATION APPROVAL FLOW
# ============================================================

status: canonical
layer: 050.flow
system: civilization-os
owner: Boss
prepared_by: Zero

purpose:
Define the canonical approval flow.

flow_steps:
1 approval-required action is detected
2 approval gate runtime materializes request
3 review or decision authority evaluates request
4 decision record is persisted
5 downstream execution proceeds only if approved
6 audit trace records full path

approval_rule:
Approval flow must remain explicit and attributable.
